                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-902504862" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="902504862">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lemon1121/">lemon</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-03-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">高中时读的 当时对诗经感兴趣 现在仍然很多首还会被 倒是唐诗忘了一干二净 呵呵</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

