  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1061750/" class="title-link">繁体竖排版，值得收藏的一本好书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1061750"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/andymao/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1148452-59.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/andymao/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">振之</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-07-30"
      class="main-meta">2006-07-30 04:15:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1061750_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  非常难得的繁体竖排版，值得收藏的一本好书，用来了解诗经的历史与对部分诗的解读都不失为一本好书。由于本书为清人所著所以需要有一点文学的功底。不然读起来会有点吃力！印刷上还算可以，不过按高要求来讲印刷质量有点不到位。所以只是推荐不力荐了

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1061750/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
